American Stock Exchange composite index, which is dominated by
smaller companies, fell 1.78 to 714.79.
</P>
<P>
Technology shares posted some of the day's steepest losses as
some third-quarter results continued to be disappointing.
</P>
<P>
As bonds rose today, the yield on the 30-year Treasury fell as
low as 6.36 percent from late Friday's 6.42 percent. 
