<HEADLINE> 8 Kidnapped, 1 Killed in Southern Philippines </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, October 15 (Xinhua) -- Armed men wearing masks
kidnapped eight men and killed another today in a village near
Isabela, Basilan province, the southern Philippines.
</P>
<P>
