when they were stopped along a highway by the armed men. All the
passengers were asked to line up along the road.
</P>
<P>
The abductors selected nine men from the passengers and allowed
the others to go unharmed. One of the selected was shot dead when
he tried to escape.
</P>
<P>
The police can not ascertain the number of passengers who were
freed as they each went their way after being told to leave.
Neither can the police get the identities of the kidnap victims,
Abdullah said.  
