<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Results of Southeast Asian Games (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, October 15 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results of
finals at the 19th Southeast Asian Games on Wednesday:
</P>
<P>
Men's Cycling:
</P>
<P>
200-meter sprint:
</P>
<P>
1. Rosman Alwi, Malaysia
</P>
<P>
2. Narrochman, Indonesia
