ceremony of the Slovak Economic Exhibition that began here today.
</P>
<P>
Poland is currently the sixth trade partner of Slovakia. The
trade volume between the two countries is expected to total 518
million U.S. dollars, up 18.3 percent over last year, according to
Cesnek. 
